<li><strong>Rochester, Minn.:</strong>&nbsp;<a href="https://sportsmedicine.mayoclinic.org/expert/adam-tagliero/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">Adam Tagliero,&nbsp;&nbsp;M.D.</a>, Sports medicine/orthopedic specialist, Mayo Clinic</li>



